text:
Sekarang masih perlu isi ulang kah miss

trans:
Now do I still need to top up, miss?
*You must complete the assigned tasks, once the tasks are completed you can withdraw like before, and you can receive the balance and commission within 5 minutes*
*This is a continuous task and after completing it you will be able to withdraw your capital and commissions*
*Now you need to make a payment of IDR 3,000,000 with a commission of IDR 1,500,000 to complete the task this time*
okay, wait miss
ss the proof of the top-up
done miss
alright please wait for 3 members to complete their top-ups
okay, miss I'll wait
please complete the top-up as soon as possible to avoid any long delays
It means that we'll transfer again and then withdraw it all at once, right?
Yes that's correct
Then how much is the third one, miss?
You have completed the first payment so now you need to complete the second and third payments combined into one total of IDR 3,000.00. To save time, we'll complete it all at once together
